g.\n\nHOOKER-TREE CONNECTIONS — 11 across Hooker and Talcott branches, concentrated in medicine and graduate education:\n\nMEDICINE:\n- HD04886 Dr. Sarah Hooker Knutti (Hopkins School of Medicine)\n- I00334 Doctor James Shepherd (Hopkins Hospital)\n- HD1183 Doctor George Burton Gilbert\n- I00276 Agnes Boxley Newton Hollerith\n\nBALTIMORE FAMILY CLUSTER (overlaps with Brown Memorial Presbyterian INST147):\n- I01138 Bayard Turnbull (Baltimore architect)\n- I01141 Jerome Herrick Tyson 'Jerry' Kidder (Baltimore Gas & Electric)\n\nWOOLSEY FAMILY CLUSTER:\n- HD1236 Alexander Hamilton 'Sandy' Woods Woolsey\n- HD2073 John Mumford Woolsey (Federal Judge — Ulysses obscenity trial 1933)\n\nOTHERS:\n- HD1342 Sophia Joanna Hill Stratton\n-\n- X02091 Jean Alexandra McCain Morgan\n\nHopkins's Baltimore location made it the natural medical and graduate destination for the Jones-Sparhawk Baltimore family cluster centered around Brown Memorial Presbyterian Church (INST147) — TD0240 Rev. John Sparhawk Jones's founding pastorate 1870+."}},"crossConnections":[]}